    <string name="mainScreenHelp"><b>Main Screen Help</b>\n
        Search Button: Will redirect you to search for a Recipe, Cuisine, Meal Types or Ingredients.\n
        Create Button: Will redirect you to create a Recipe, Cuisine, Meal Types or Ingredients.\n
        Favourites Button: Will redirect you to see your favourite recipes.\n
        Shopping Cart Button: Will redirect you to see your current shopping cart, which contains
        ingredients added to the shopping cart.</string>
